title: DWARVEN LAST STAND - Third Age Total War Gameplay
description:
For 3 long days the Dwarves have been marching, trying to escape the reach of a huge Isengard army.  But the have run out of supplies and are growing tired!  They must stand their ground and FIGHT!  Enjoy this epic battle in Third Age Total War!

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
